==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Loving cup
<hw>Lov"ing cup`</hw>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>A large ornamental drinking
vessel having two or more handles, intended to pass from hand to hand,
as at a banquet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>an award resembling a <er>loving cup</er>{1} that is
given to the winner of a competition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Loving-kindness</ent>⟦br⟧
